title: NOAA, Tsunami significant wave heights in Pacific ocean, 20:00-21:00 GMT, Feb 27, 2010
name: NOAA, Tsunami significant wave heights in Pacific ocean, 20:00-21:00 GMT, Feb 27, 2010
description:
The point shapefile is based on National Data Buoy Center (NDBC) buoy data.
You may find similar data for each hour between 9:00 GMT and 22:00 GMT 
eleswhere on finder! Search with keyword "NDBC", "wave height". Please note that
the data compiled by NDBC is a snapshot of what is reported by NDBC and the set
of buoys reporting varies from one hour to next.

author.source: National Data Buoy Center, NOAA website
